This paper discusses a method for efficiently eliciting scalar annotations for dataset construction and system quality estimation. The focus is on natural language processing (NLP) tasks, which fall under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses machine learning techniques for ranking and classification, which are relevant to sub-categories such as machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and computer vision (cs.CV).
